{"tid":1185602,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"係仁濟醫院做工程既人真係好慘","createTime":"2019-06-04T10:59:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-30T10:23:28.000Z","uid":32950,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"73ccafd43f2ec3b62a83f0bbee62568fb5d258d6","tid":1185602,"uid":32950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T10:59:52.000Z","msg":"話說，我係仁濟醫院二樓做x光<br />\n隔離間房做緊工程，咁我都無咩理<br />\n點知無啦啦有個女人勁大聲咁鬧人<br />\n成個癲婆咁，鬧到成層樓都聽到<br />\n我就伸過頭望下佢就見到三條友，包括個癲婆<br />\n重有後面個兩條友<br />\n就係到叉住條腰係咁屌<br />\n因為見到佢地有掛牌仔<br />\n應該係醫院d大粒野黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我見係間房岀黎既人都面如死灰<br />\n見到佢地咁心都痛埋<br />\n大家都係做野姐，駛唔駛屌到咁盡<br />\n我唔知其他醫院d大粒野係點<br />\n不過荃灣仁濟醫院d大粒野真係好差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係個到做野既人都好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59ce2d5113499c3b9fc519b099da9e27906c0800","tid":1185602,"uid":118709,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T11:28:29.000Z","msg":"因為咩事鬧人先 講到冇頭冇尾咁你叫我地連登仔點做網絡判官呀"},{"pid":"7794feef10dbb124c1ea9fa21fae47f26811409d","tid":1185602,"uid":185066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T11:30:03.000Z","msg":"關工程呢行咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7290e1fb09ee15881ee7a4243a7772c09db22feb","tid":1185602,"uid":165958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T11:33:30.000Z","msg":"可能樓主就係做工程果個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2ea41afe1f6c359899eaa8ca77a18d249cf7bd8","tid":1185602,"uid":20376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T10:23:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}